<h1>{{ 'Frequently Asked Questions'|trans }}</h1>
<h3>{{ 'What is the purpose of this site?'|trans }}</h3>
<p>{{ 'Simple! To upload and share games from %goglink%'|trans|nl2br|replace({'%goglink%': '<a href="https://www.gog.com" target="_blank">GOG.com</a>'})|raw }}</p>
<h3>{{ 'What is the easiest way to download or extract files?'|trans }}</h3>
<p>{{ 'Please use %jdownloader2link% to download game files and %7ziplink% to extract them. It is advise to not download large files via TOR Browser as the network is slow and puts strain on it.'|trans|nl2br|replace({'%jdownloader2link%': '<a href="http://jdownloader.org/jdownloader2" target="_blank">JDownloader 2</a>', '%7ziplink%': '<a href="http://www.7-zip.org/download.html" target="_blank">7-Zip</a>'})|raw }}</p>
<h3>{{"Will you consider adding other hosters?"|trans }}</h3>
<p>{{ 'We find Zippyshare to be a decent file hoster. There are no plans at this time to add or use others.'|trans }}</p>
<p>{{ 'I can not access Zippyshare. What is going on?'|trans }}</p>
<h3>{{ 'Zippyshare is currently blocking visitors from the United Kingdom. You can use VPN to bypass the block.'|trans }}</h3>
<h3>{{ 'How are download links prevented from expiring?'|trans }}</h3>
<p>{{ 'All games are avaiable to be voted on for a re-uploaded 30 days after they were last uploaded to guard against dead links.'|trans }}</p>
<h3>{{ 'How can I support the site?'|trans }}</h3>
<p>{{ 'Finding bugs is one way! If you run into any issues or notice anything out of place, please open an issue on <a href="https://github.com/MachineGunnur/gg" target="_blank">GitHub</a>.'|trans }}</p>
